This has got to be one of the most all time fish slaps! Well.. occy slap! Seriously.. what the heck 😂 #copthat #occyslap Still laughing as we repost this from the good folks at @goproanz. Always keep a GoPro on you - Meanwhile in New Zealand... 🐙 Caption this for your chance to earn a #GoProHERO7 Black. 👇
🎬 #GoProFamily member @barekiwi + @TaiyoMasuda @kaikourakayaks
@PureNewZealand #NZMustDo

We just love people like @chrisburkard that venture beyond the boundaries of comfort and cliches to capture moments like this. Just take a second and put yourself in his shoes or the surfers shoes (10mm booties 😬) and be thankful that you get to see moments like this without freezing your toosh off!
@chrisburkard - I’ve photographed more days with blue skies than I can count. Honestly they all start to blend together. But some of these sessions in the Arctic have been permanently seared into my mind. You give so much more of yourself to explore & ride waves like this when it’s hovering below 0 degrees. Maybe the sacrifice is what makes it so worthwhile. Just to see what you are willing to give for a once in a lifetime experience.
